Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}独自一人叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:19.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:23.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:29.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}广阔的大地上 一粒种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:32.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸展开根系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:40.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又结出青色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:45.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:48.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:52.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:55.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:59.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
